            "id": "687960d7096227000197b6ef",
            "title": "$100 Invested In T-Mobile US 10 Years Ago Would Be Worth This Much Today",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-fmEAfK gfWgFw\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">T-Mobile US <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"TMUS\" style=\"display:inline-block\">TMUS</span> has outperformed the market over the past 10 years by 8.15% on an annualized basis producing an average annual return of 19.66%. Currently, T-Mobile US has a market capitalization of $257.78 billion. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Buying $100 In TMUS:</strong> If an investor had bought $100 of TMUS stock 10 years ago, it would be worth <strong>$603.32</strong> today based on a price of $227.03 for TMUS at the time of writing.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-jPaQzP cneWpx\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold\">Trending Investment Opportunities</div><div class=\"flex items-end justify-end\"><div class=\"text-right text-sm bg-gray-200 rounded px-2 py-1\">Advertisement</div></div></div><div class=\"cta-stacked GalleryCarousel_splide_slidewrap__zHpTC\"><div class=\"sc-FhnSQ kphHWf carousel-container\"><div aria-label=\"Carousel\" class=\"splide\"><div class=\"splide-track-wrapper\"><div class=\"splide__track\"><ul class=\"splide__list\"><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"carousel-pagination\"><div class=\"splide__arrows\"><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev page-left-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"